Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.30,OPEDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}回憶映照於上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:24.36,OPEDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}架起了七色的絲帶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:29.36,OPEDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}單獨一人的話  很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:31.74,OPEDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心情不好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:38.07,OPEDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}無論何時  都請留在我身邊
